data.headline: S&P 500, Dow, Nasdaq, and Russell 2000 all opened higher following upbeat January payroll numbers
bullets: January jobs report showed a 130,000 payroll gain and unemployment falling to 4.3%, both beating forecasts

Traders closely watching moves in the US dollar and Treasury yields after the report
